quran[5{c,v,t}:
6,147,ab agar woh tumhejjhutlainto un se keh do ke tumahray rab ka daman rehmat wasee hai aur mujrimon se is ke azaab ko phera nahi ja sakta
6,148,"yeh mushriq log ( tumhari un baton ke jawab mein ) zaroor kahin ge ke"" agar Allah chahta to nah hum shirk karte aur nah hamaray baap dada, aur nah hum kisi cheez ko haraam thrate"" aisi hi baatein bana bana kar inn se pehlay ke logon ne bhi jhtlaya tha yahan taq ke aakhir-kaar hamaray azaab ka maza unhon ne chakh liya un se kaho"" kya tumahray paas koi ilm hai jisay hamaray samnay paish krsko? tum to mehez gumaan par chal rahay ho aur nari qiyaas aarayyan karte ho """
6,149,"phir kaho ( tumhari is Hujjat ke muqaabla mein )"" haqeeqat ras Hujjat to Allah ke paas hai, be shak agar Allah chahta to tum sab ko hadaayat day deta """
6,150,"un se kaho ke"" lao apne woh gawah jo is baat ki shahadat den ke Allah hi ne inn cheezon ko haraam kya hai"" phir agar woh shahadat day den to tum un ke sath shahadat nah dena, aur hargiz unn logon ki khwahisaat ke peechay nah chalna jinhon ne hamari ayaat ko jhtlaya hai, aur jo akhirat ke munkir hain, aur jo dosaron ko apne rab ka humsar banatay hain"
6,151,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! un se kaho ke aao mein tumhe sunaoon tumahray rab ne tum par kya pabandiyan aed ki hain : yeh ke is ke sath kisi ko shareek nah karo, aur walidain ke sath naik sulooq karo, aur apni aulaad ko muflisi ke dar se qatal nah karo, hum tumhe bhi rizaq dete hain aur a noon ko bhi den ge aur be sharmi ki baton ke qareeb bhi nah jao khuwa woh khuli hon ya chhupi aur kisi jaan ko jisay Allah ne mohtaramTehraya hai halaak nah karo magar haq ke sath yeh baatein hain jin ki hadaayat is ne tumhe ki hai, shayad ke tum samajh boojh se kaam lau"
